Package: planisphere
Title: Map projections
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Nicolas", "Lambert", email = "nicolas.lambert@cnrs.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4976-6560")))
Description: A wrapper around D3.js for cartographic projections to design and visualize world maps (planispheres). Projections are computed using D3.js spherical geometry rather than ellipsoidal geodesic models. 
License: GPL-3
URL: https://neocarto.github.io/planisphere/
BugReports: https://github.com/neocarto/planisphere/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    sf,
    V8,
    geojsonsf
Suggests:
    knitr,
    r2d3
Language: en-US
